[normal]&#xa0;&#xa0; 
[normal]Successive governments have moved to curb the rising cost of 
[normal]housing benefit
[normal] by adjusting benefit
[normal] entitlement,
[normal] but these efforts have focused on treating the symptoms rather than the cause.
[normal] While this submission makes recommendations to mitigate against the worst effects of these welfare reforms, t
[normal]he Government must invest
[normal] in 
